						<summary>

						<p>Records gift, by <hi rend="bold">Komāra Hambīradēva-Mahāpātrulu</hi> to the servants of god Rājanārāyaṇadēva of <hi rend="bold">Bejavāḍa,</hi> of the village of <hi rend="bold">Venakepāḍu</hi> with all sources of enjoyment. Mentions the previous gift of the village to the same god by <hi rend="bold">Kulōttuṅgachōḍayadēva-Mahārāja.</hi></p>						

